### From v4.0.x to v4.1.0

```bash
# Automatic migration
./payload/install.sh --upgrade

# Manual verification
/version 4.1.0 --dry-run
```

**Changes Required:**
- Update installer references from `installer/` to `payload/`
- Verify Claude output styles integration
- Test enhanced template processing

### From v3.x to v4.1.0

```bash
